  "text": "## 1. DEFINITIONS & KEY TERMS  \n- **\"Account\"** = Your SmartSaver savings account held with FirstUK Bank\n- **\"We/Our/Us\"** = FirstUK Bank PLC and its employees\n- **\"You/Your\"** = The customer opening the account (account holder)\n- **\"Business Day\"** = Monday–Friday (excluding UK bank holidays)\n- **\"Deposit\"** = Money you place into the account\n- **\"Withdrawal\"** = Money you remove from the account\n- **\"Interest\"** = Money we pay you based on your balance (variable rate)  \n---",
